data.description: Stunning freshly renovated first floor 2 bedroom, 2 full bathroom home. Located in the beautiful Coral Palms community. Recent upgrades include new kitchen cabinets, granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and tile floors throughout. Step into an open floor plan, with ample separation between the bedrooms, a private covered patio, and plenty of room for storage.   HOA fee includes sewer water and trash, dog park, security cameras, community pool & spa. BBQ area. Call today to schedule a tour!
